'''布罗德曼6区'''（英文：Brodmann area 6），简称'''BA6'''，是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的一个细胞结构分区<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Brodmann Area 6 - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-6|access-date=2022-05-05|work=ScienceDirect|archive-date=2022-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505183312/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-6}}</ref>。布罗德曼6区在[[额叶|额叶]]的外侧，它由上而下分别与布罗德曼[[布罗德曼8区|8区]]，[[布罗德曼9区|9区]]，和[[布罗德曼44区|44区]]毗邻，它的位置位于布罗德曼4区的前部<ref name=":0" />。

== 结构 ==
BA6横跨额叶的外侧和内侧。BA6对外侧最靠下的部分位于[[中央前回|中央前回]]没有被[[布罗德曼4区|4区]]占据的部分。BA6的外侧的上方的部分位于[[额上回|额上回]]和[[额中回|额中回]]的后部。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Glial tumors in brodmann area 6: spread pattern and relationships to motor areas|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25969935/|last=Shah|first=Komal B.|last2=Hayman|first2=L. Anne|date=2015-05|journal=Radiographics: A Review Publication of the Radiological Society of North America, Inc|issue=3|doi=10.1148/rg.2015140207|volume=35|pages=793–803|issn=1527-1323|pmc=4450978|pmid=25969935|last3=Chavali|first3=Lakshmi S.|last4=Hamilton|first4=Jackson D.|last5=Prabhu|first5=Sujit S.|last6=Wangaryattawanich|first6=Pattana|last7=Kumar|first7=Vinodh A.|last8=Kumar|first8=Ashok J.|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2022-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220620050430/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25969935/}}</ref>

布罗德曼6区也成为“无颗粒6区”（agranular area 6）。这是因为该区域与其他[[大脑皮质|大脑皮质]]的细胞结构分区不同，缺少内颗粒层（即IV层）。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The importance of being agranular: a comparative account of visual and motor cortex|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15937013/|last=Shipp|first=Stewart|date=2005-04-29|journal=Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Biological Sciences|issue=1456|doi=10.1098/rstb.2005.1630|volume=360|pages=797–814|issn=0962-8436|pmc=1569485|pmid=15937013|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2022-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505183618/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15937013/}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
从功能的角度来说，布罗德曼6区包含[[前运动区|前运动区]]和[[运动辅助区|运动辅助区]]。其中，前运动皮层位于额叶的外侧面，而运动辅助区位于额叶的内侧面。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The role of rostral Brodmann area 6 in mental-operation tasks: an integrative neuroimaging approach|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12379604/|last=Hanakawa|first=Takashi|last2=Honda|first2=Manabu|date=2002-11|journal=Cerebral Cortex (New York, N.Y.: 1991)|issue=11|doi=10.1093/cercor/12.11.1157|volume=12|pages=1157–1170|issn=1047-3211|pmid=12379604|last3=Sawamoto|first3=Nobukatsu|last4=Okada|first4=Tomohisa|last5=Yonekura|first5=Yoshiharu|last6=Fukuyama|first6=Hidena|last7=Shibasaki|first7=Hiroshi|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2022-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505183316/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12379604/}}</ref>

